23
00:02:01,010 --> 00:02:04,010
Act 8:
A Night in Boulogne

24
00:02:23,600 --> 00:02:25,130
This is bad...

25
00:02:25,740 --> 00:02:26,930
Albert!

26
00:02:27,840 --> 00:02:29,640
W-What are you barging in here for?!

27
00:02:29,940 --> 00:02:34,070
I'm sorry. I kept calling, but you didn't answer.

28
00:02:34,980 --> 00:02:37,350
You have a visitor from the Champs Elysees.

29
00:02:38,580 --> 00:02:39,520
The Count?

30
00:02:39,750 --> 00:02:43,190
His Excellency says that he does not wish to see you today.

31
00:02:43,620 --> 00:02:45,220
Did he give you a message or something?

32
00:02:45,220 --> 00:02:47,120
No, Monsieur, nothing in particular.

33
00:02:47,860 --> 00:02:48,830
I see...

34
00:02:49,730 --> 00:02:50,490
What's this?

35
00:02:50,600 --> 00:02:52,890
His Excellency wishes to unveil his new villa.

36
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:56,490
That is an invitation to a dinner party.
By all means, bring your entire family.

37
00:02:57,130 --> 00:02:59,530
With pleasure!
Where is the villa?

38
00:03:00,140 --> 00:03:02,470
The forest of Auteuil.

39
00:03:03,270 --> 00:03:04,800
He has a villa in that gloomy place?

40
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:09,270
Yes. His Excellency insisted on this villa in particular.

41
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:31,060
If I'm not mistaken, Monsieur Villefort used to own this villa.

42
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:33,630
It's almost fallen to ruin.

43
00:03:34,140 --> 00:03:38,230
While his first wife was still alive,
it was a bright, cheerful place.

44
00:03:38,740 --> 00:03:42,110
You mean Valentine's real mother?

45
00:03:42,710 --> 00:03:45,580
She was still so young and beautiful when she died.

46
00:04:06,470 --> 00:04:08,170
Thank you for coming.

47
00:04:09,370 --> 00:04:10,700
My lord General.

48
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:12,740
Thank you for inviting us.

49
00:04:19,250 --> 00:04:20,480
Count!

50
00:04:21,450 --> 00:04:24,010
Well, well! The good
Madame Villefort!

51
00:04:25,090 --> 00:04:26,650
